17 SECTION 3. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
18 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 1003 of Title 40, unless there
19 is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
20 There is hereby created in the State Treasury a revolving fund
21 for the Department of Labor, to be designated the “Oklahoma Wrecker
22 and Towing Services Revolving Fund”. The fund shall be a continuing
23 fund not subject to fiscal year limitations. All monies accruing to
24 the credit of the fund are hereby appropriated and shall be budgeted
Req. No. 16927 Page 12

1 and expended by the Department of Labor for the purpose of
2 administering the Oklahoma Wrecker Services Division. Expenditures
3 from the fund shall be made upon warrants issued by the State
4 Treasurer against claims filed as prescribed by law with the
5 Director of the Office of Management and Enterprise Services for
6 approval and payment.
